Interface ReviewSummary

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ABLinkable, Editable, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity, gw.pl.external.entity.KeyableEntity, Retireable, Versionable
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface ReviewSummary
extends ABLinkable, Retireable, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity
    A summary of a service provider review, created from a given Review in ClaimCenter.
